remarks.format: ## Remarks 此集上的突变生成新的组。Mutations on this set generate new sets. 对一组增量更改同时允许垃圾回收清理不再引用任何唯一的一组数据，尽可能使用与之前版本的一组共享尽可能多的内存。Incremental changes to a set share as much memory as possible with the prior versions of a set, while allowing garbage collection to clean up any unique set data that is no longer being referenced.
